 2023-03632023-04-21AAFC
ActFarm Products Agencies Act
SubjectProclamation Amending the Chicken Farmers of Canada Proclamation
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue AMENDING THE CHICKEN FARMERS OF CANADA PROCLAMATION in order to (1) remove section 9 of the Proclamation as it is beyond the powers of the Act; (2) provide a timeframe for payment in the marketing plan as prescribed in section 36 of the Act; (3) amend certain definitions; and (4) update the names of the Commodity Boards.
